@startuml m4-cluster-aware-operator-sequence
skinparam dpi 300
title M4 — BEAM-Cluster-Aware Operator + Health Bridge

participant "K8s API" as API
participant "BEAM operator\n(Bonny)" as OP
participant "Horde / Erlang\ndistribution" as H
participant "pod" as POD

== reconcile loop ==
OP -> H: watch membership
H --> OP: members + handoff state
OP -> API: set pod readiness gate\n(custom condition = member Up)

== scale-down ==
API -> POD: terminate (finalizer / preStop)
POD -> OP: handoff complete?
OP -> H: drain + hand off processes
H --> OP: done
OP -> API: clear finalizer (allow delete)
note over API #ccffcc: pod kept in endpoints until member healthy;\nnot deleted until handoff done
@enduml
